title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1644-1.1 - Debt service defined
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1644-1.1 - Debt service defined

State Regulations

Debt service as used in this Subchapter refers to the
periodic provisions for payment of principal and interest on the outstanding
indebtedness of the local agency. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
1644-1.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
